Brave heart

Boeing’s CEO, David Calhoun, will step down at the end of 2024.

His four years in the top job were marked by
safety scandals, grounded planes, the pandemic and more grounded planes.
波音公司首席执行官戴维·卡尔霍恩 (David Calhoun) 将于 2024 年底辞职。
他担任首席执行官的四年充满了安全丑闻、飞机停飞、新冠疫情和更多飞机停飞。

