===
Phil NYC

If you're worried about the risks of flying on a Boeing 737, you're never going to want to drive a car again.
The chances of being killed in a car accident at some point in your life is 1 in 93 .
You have a 1 in 816,545,929 chance of dying in a plane crash.

如果您担心乘坐波音 737 的风险，您将永远不想再开车。
在您一生中的某个时刻，死于车祸的几率是 93 分之一。
您死于飞机失事的几率为 816,545,929 分之一。

