SK Charoaborty:

John Barnett was the Boeing whistleblower.
His life was in danger and he knew it.
Someone arranged for his death and made it appear as a suicide.
Justice must be done to a honest and brave man.
He must not be just forgotten.

约翰·巴尼特是波音公司的举报人。他的生命处于危险之中，他知道这一点。
有人安排了他的死亡，并使其看起来像是自杀。
正义必须给予诚实勇敢的人。

